author: Russell Brand
description:
The CIA just admitted Lee Harvey Oswald was involved in a psychological warfare operation before JFK’s assassination—and that’s not a theory, it’s in the documents. After decades of lies, denials, and distractions, we’re finally getting fragments of the truth. But if this is what they’re admitting now… what else are they hiding?
